name: Spiral bracelet/necklace
description:
This simple design makes a very fun bracelet, whatever your age.

Three color patterns are shown in the picture, but you can pick your own if you want (including the basic silver color)! If you do, please use the Contact link over there ----------->

It can also be made into a necklace. I suggest one that's long enough to slip over your head, so that you don't need to worry about a clasp. (If you'd like a smaller one than that, the price will be lower than what's listed.)

name: Xmas Tree earrings
description:
These cute little Christmas trees (along with everything else I sell) are lighter than they look.

You're sure to get compliments on them when you wear them to parties this holiday season; when you do, please tell people where you bought them!

name: Silver Byzantine bracelet
description:
Silver catches the light in amazing ways, and this intricate pattern on a thin band allows it to glint just right.

This pattern can also be done in copper, aluminum, or any pattern of colors; if this option is chosen, the price would be $35.

If you want to specify colors or size, or just ask a question, please use the "Contact" form over there --------->

name: Black Ice necklace
description:
This lovely 18-inch necklace is the perfect highlight for a low-cut dress, and could also work over a sweater.

I designed this chain specifically to complement the pendant, which I picked up in Seattle!

name: Stretchy bracelet
description:
Go clasp-free! Some of the connecting rings in these bracelets are made of rubber (EPDM, latex-free), so you can just stretch them over your hand!

These come in plenty of different colors. They can also be done in a denser weave, for a much smoother feel.

If you want to specify colors or size, or just ask a question, please use the "Contact" form over there --------->
